{"tid":114974,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"突然好想搵人傾下先發覺冇人可以搵","createTime":"2017-02-10T08:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T04:33:36.000Z","uid":47480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2552078d8a0097674e5be56a259fe0dc272310d1","tid":114974,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"上年一直覺得個人唔係好掂，襯過完年得閒去左做檢查，諗住都幾十歲人，係時候check下，星期一姑娘已經打黎叫我盡快黎醫院睇報告，但有啲驚，正常你冇事邊會叫你返去睇報告，拖到尋日先去睇。<br />\n<br />\n結果： 有病，咩病就唔講，嚴重到幾乎接近末期。<br />\n<br />\n如果剩係食藥㩒住，應該仲有7-10年壽命，但有機會惡化，最壞情況得3-5年。<br />\n<br />\n如果做手術，只係穩定到病情，冇得復原返正常功能，手術後定期要覆診，正常飲食同運動既話，極低機會惡化，但手術費好貴同埋做完手術基本上半年唔返得工。<br />\n<br />\n其實我心入面都有答案，只係好唏噓發生都算幾大件事，想搵人講又唔知搵咩人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7611c8a47e1a6f713f9006e1e892c466085ba818","tid":114974,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"捱義氣聽你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5d2f66c6fa73965cfb834e3f3c227a95378fc6","tid":114974,"uid":3974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"加油⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2184e59bd6b6b1366ed02f160edde6849e1fba2c","tid":114974,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"巴打講啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd59a62b8d671b6fac57509fcf178d00a100f09","tid":114974,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:57:40.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意講係邊方面嘅病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9d3d4342e28a78502ac203b5bfaee466f85536","tid":114974,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"諗住點？"},{"pid":"2dac48334d5dbfb36108abf949dcefdb7ee6c69b","tid":114974,"uid":32113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,